narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This course is great for both dance lovers and for those who know nothing about dance. It teaches you to be a more observant writer and to translate the visual into the written.
Watching dance performances and attempting interesting creative/critical writing about them, including two live performances.
This class was very interesting. It served as both a glimpse of the history of dance and a way to improve one's own writing.
